<li><a href="https://github.com/gofiber/keyauth">keyauth</a><a data-role="trackawesomelist-badge" href="https://github.com/gofiber/keyauth" style="text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;"><span style="color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;"><span style="padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;">stars</span><span style="padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;">58</span></span></a><!--TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_START____{"type":"repo","stargazerCount":58,"repo":"gofiber/keyauth"}____TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_END--> - Key auth middleware provides a key based authentication.</li>
<li><a href="https://github.com/gofiber/rewrite">rewrite</a><a data-role="trackawesomelist-badge" href="https://github.com/gofiber/rewrite" style="text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;"><span style="color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;"><span style="padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;">stars</span><span style="padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;">12</span></span></a><!--TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_START____{"type":"repo","stargazerCount":12,"repo":"gofiber/rewrite"}____TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_END--> - Rewrite middleware rewrites the URL path based on provided rules. It can be helpful for backward compatibility or just creating cleaner and more descriptive links.</li>
<li><a href="https://github.com/gofiber/storage">storage</a><a data-role="trackawesomelist-badge" href="https://github.com/gofiber/storage" style="text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;"><span style="color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;"><span style="padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;">stars</span><span style="padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;">136</span></span></a><!--TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_START____{"type":"repo","stargazerCount":136,"repo":"gofiber/storage"}____TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_END--> - Premade storage drivers that implement the Storage interface, designed to be used with various Fiber middlewares.</li>
<li><a href="https://github.com/gofiber/template">template</a><a data-role="trackawesomelist-badge" href="https://github.com/gofiber/template" style="text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;"><span style="color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;"><span style="padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;">stars</span><span style="padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;">164</span></span></a><!--TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_START____{"type":"repo","stargazerCount":164,"repo":"gofiber/template"}____TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_END--> - This package contains 8 template engines that can be used with Fiber v1.10.x Go version 1.13 or higher is required.</li>
